estului creditorului privat prudent.</span></span></span></span><span style="display:none" class="S_PCT_SHORT" id="id_pctA380_short" onMouseOver="marcheaza(id_pctA380_short,id_pctA380)" onMouseOut="demarcheaza(id_pctA380_short,id_pctA380)" onMouseDown="plusMinus(id_pctA380_short,id_pctA380_bdy)"> ... </span></span><span class="S_PCT" style="display: block; color:black;" id="id_pctA384"><span class="S_PCT_TTL" id="id_pctA384_ttl" onMouseOver="marcheaza(id_pctA384_ttl,id_pctA384)" onMouseOut="demarcheaza(id_pctA384_ttl,id_pctA384)" onMouseDown="plusMinus(id_pctA384_short,id_pctA384_bdy)">2.<!----></span> <span class="S_PCT_BDY" id="id_pctA384_bdy">La <A href="~/../../../Public/DetaliiDocumentAfis/227275">articolul 22, alineatul (1)</A> va avea următorul cuprins:<span class="S_CIT"><span class="S_ART" style="display: block; color:black;" id="id_artA386" name="id_artA386"><span class="TAG_COLLAPSED" id="id_cllpsdA386" onMouseOver="marcheaza(id_cllpsdA386,id_artA386)" onMouseOut="demarcheaza(id_cllpsdA386,id_artA386)" onMouseDown="plusMinus(id_artA386_bdy,id_cllpsdA386)">
